about

Who do you call when you need help with ghosts? Ghostbusters.

Who do you call when you need help with that pesky showerhead or drain in your home that you can't quite figure out? Your dad.

And who do you call for help with all your major web design and development needs? Us!

We're Dad Designs, founded by a group of young developers who wanted to create a brand collective focused on web development services with the same concept of reliability. The internet is a scary place, just like life. If you need assistance, you should have a source you can trust to provide you with reliable help, every time.

We're a group of top developers, designers, marketers, and creatives who have been in the industry for over 8 years - so we know what we're doing, don't worry!

Besides full web development, we offer a wide range of other internet-savvy services, such as graphic design, app development, video editing animation, social media marketing, search engine optimization, and content writing.

Our team has a passion for doing what we do best, which is using our skills to help people like you succeed in their own business.
